---
title: Easy Cheesy Spiced Chicken & Potato Wedges with Pear Salad & Dill-Parsley Mayo
description: Simple, indulgent flavours are the highlight of this modern dish. With mouth-watering chicken strips coated in
our popular Aussie spice blend and gooey Cheddar cheese, plus with roasted wedges giving a filling finish, we
think you'll be licking the plate clean.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
